         keep  test.e         mcopy arcade.macrostest     start         phk                            get code bank for data bank         plb                            to access code data easily         lda   >$E0C029                 save old video registor value         sta   SaveVideoRegister         lda   >$E0C029                 save shadow register         sta   SaveShadowRegister         lda   #%0000000001000000       linerize SHR         ora   >$E0C029         lda   #%0000000001011111       turn off shadowing         ora   >$E0C035         lda   #%0000000010000000       display SHR         ora   >$E0C029;insert code here;all done lets quit         lda   SaveVideoRegister        restore video registor         sta   >$E0C029         lda   SaveShadowRegister       restore shadow register         sta   >$E0C035         lda   #0                       indicate to shell no errors         _Quit QuitData                 return to calling programQuitData dc    i4'0'                    quit back to calling program         dc    i'0'                     no restart from memorySaveVideoRegister ds 2                  Video registor register save spaceSaveShadowRegister ds 2         end